title: Vampire Weekend Debut Album
description:
Vampire Weekend is the debut album from New York City rock band Vampire Weekend. It was released on January 29, 2008 through XL Recordings. In the US, the album sold over 27,000 copies in its first week, debuting at #17 on the Billboard album charts. The album also debuted at #22 on the UK chart and reached #99 in Australia.
